<title><![CDATA[ China&#039;s PLA to become most modern military by 2020: Report]]></title>
<link><![CDATA[ http://zeenews.india.com/news/world/chinas-pla-to-become-most-modern-military-by-2020-report_1884726.html ]]></link>
<description><![CDATA[  China aims to complete the reform of its 2.3-million-strong army and have the most modern armed forces capable of 'informationised warfare' by 2020, laying a solid foundation for the PLA to become a world-class force, according to the new five-year military development plan.
 ]]></description>
